<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><presentation>v1 v2 </presentation>
<title>Fill my cup, Lord</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Fyll mitt beger,
 Gud jeg ber Deg,
 slukk den tørst
 som brenner i min sjel.
 Brød fra himlen
 metter hele mitt begjær.
 Fyll meg Gud, fyll meg nå
 og gjør alt vel.

[V2]
 Fill my cup, Lord,
 I lift it up, Lord.
 Come and quench
 this thirsting of my soul.
 Bread of heaven, Feed me
 till I want no more.
 Fill my cup, fill it up and
 make me whole.</lyrics>
<key>G</key>
<aka>Fyll mitt beger</aka>
</song>